cd C:\Code\strongswan
docker-compose -f docker-compose.gmssl.yml up -d
```

**自动化部署** (云端 + 本地):
```powershell
# Windows PowerShell - 完整自动化
.\deployment-scripts\deploy-server.ps1
```

